title: I  have already own the Riot Kayle. But I did not recieve anything in 10 years anniversary. Why?

replies.body: You haven't received anything because we're not done sending out gifts just yet!  The gift will be a mystery, so I can't make it Riot Graves- sorry!  Stay up to date on our progress via the [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hopefully luck will be in your favor!
Thank you for reply！ So I will get a reminder when I receive the gift， right?{{item:3902}}
